    var items = new List
    {
        new Item { SKU = "AAD_BASIC" },
        new Item { SKU = "RIGHTSMANAGEMENT" },
        new Item { SKU = "MCOPSTNC" }
    };
}

The template is rendered with items supplied by a foreach statement:
@foreach (var item in items)
{
    @itemTemplate(item)
}
Rendered output:
Item SKU: AAD_BASIC.
Item SKU: RIGHTSMANAGEMENT.
Item SKU: MCOPSTNC.

